event.title: First meet-up of the new Fellowshipgroup in Z端rich, Switzerland
event.body: On Thursday, March 6th, at 6pm there will be a first meet-up of the Z端rich Fellowshipgroup since renewing. Invited are all supporters of Free Software as well as other interested persons. As this is the first meet-up, we will mainly discuss about self organisation and further activities. The meeting will be in Stampfenbachstrasse 69, E-Stock, ID-Lounge (ETH Z端rich). Who will not be able to make it in time, is of course invited to join later.
